These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, canadian, brazilian, polish
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking, collecting, chess
City: rome, boston, miami, colone
House: art-deco, farmhouse, colonial, wooden
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 2. the canadian is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the colonial house is on the right of the canadian##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 7. the brazilian is on the left of the canadian##1
 8. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Nationality    | brazilian   | canadian       | german | polish   |
| Hobby        | cooking    | chess  | collecting      | filmmaking |
| City         | colone      | boston | miami         | rome   |
| House   | art-deco | farmhouse       | colonial        | wooden   |

