.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, go, whist
City: rome, berlin, venice, london
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, superhero, scientific
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, camping, board-games, cooking
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person playing domino is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing bridge is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Game           | domino | bridge | whist | go |
| City   | rome  | venice | berlin         | london      |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero      | comedy    | scientific         | action   |
| Hobby     | skydiving         | camping    | cooking          | board-games         |

