.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, drama, adventure, crime
House: craftsman, victorian, palace, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, chinese, german
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, iced-tea, tea
 1. the palace house is the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 4. the chinese is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the german is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 7. the craftsman house is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the colombian is between the person drinking iced-tea and the victorian house##2
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | drama | crime  | horror | adventure      |
| House   | craftsman       | futuristic    | victorian      | palace      |
| Nationality           | german     | colombian     | brazilian         | chinese   |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | 7up | sprite     | tea |

