.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, cain, bluemaster, aristoff
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, horse, goldfish
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, filmmaking, fishing
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, poker, go
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the old-henry-smoker and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | aristoff | old-henry | bluemaster     | cain       |
| Pet          | hamster   | goldfish    | horse | goat       |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks     | sudoku       | fishing    | filmmaking     |
| Game         | poker  | go  | snooker | mah-jongg |

