 4. the italian is on the far right##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is between the fisherman and the manager##2
 6. the photographer is on the right of the british##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 8. the italian is the swisher-smoker##1
 9. the thai is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
10. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
11. the british is the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre    | country   | punk | r&b | rock      |
