 2. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the electrician##3
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who likes green is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 9. the person who likes green is the person playing domino##1
10. the musician is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
11. the person who likes turquise is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |     4     |
| Game      | domino      | poker  | whist | bridge      |
