1. the person who likes yellow is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
4. the fonseca-smoker is the fan of dubstep##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the person who's birthday is in january and the havana-smoker##2
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the fan of house and the tiparillo-smoker##2
9. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |      4       |
