.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dannemann, pall-mall, siglo
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, tram, roller, trike
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, chestnut, ebony, blue
4 different games are played: whist, snooker, canasta, monopoly
 1. the person who likes blue is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person driving the train is between the person who likes chestnut and the person who likes blue##2
 3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is the person who likes blue##1
 6. the havana-smoker is between the person playing canasta and the siglo-smoker##2
 7. the havana-smoker is the person playing whist##1
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
10. the person playing canasta is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |       4       |
| Cigar   | siglo    | havana  | pall-mall       | dannemann  |
| Transport     | tram    | train | roller | trike        |
| Color     | blue       | ebony     | chestnut          | lavender    |
| Game   | monopoly | whist    | canasta     | snooker |

