 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person who growslily is the game-smoker##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Color         | emerald      | blood-red | brown       | grey   |
| City   | edinburgh     | prague | san-francisco | paris |
| Cigar   | old-henry    | cain     | chaman        | game       |
| Flower     | balloon-flower | bellflower   | daffodil   | lily       |

