.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, rat, mouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
City: london, venice, hannover, rome
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, bluemaster, oliveros
 1. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the bluemaster-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
 5. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 6. the person traveling to london is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the siglo-smoker##2
 7. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person traveling to london is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Pet          | bird | mouse   | rat   | frog |
| Hobby           | video-games   | rock-climbing     | drawing   | magic-tricks |
| City   | venice    | london    | rome   | hannover   |
| Cigar         | siglo    | cain | oliveros | bluemaster    |

 